<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>-<span class="c5"> أَوْ إِرْثاً:</span> ذَكَرَ سَبَبَهُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>-<span class="c5"> أَوْ مُحَلًّى بِأَحَدِ النَّقْدَيْنِ:</span> قَوَّمَهُ بِالآخَرِ،<span class="c5"> أَوْ بِهِمَا:</span> فَبِأَيِّهِمَا شَاءَ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَإِذَا حَرَّرَهَا:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>-<span class="c5"> فَإِنْ أَقَرَّ الخَصْمُ:</span> حُكِمَ عَلَيْهِ بِسُؤَالِ مُدَّعٍ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَإِنْ أَنْكَرَ وَلَا بَيِّنَةَ:</span> فَقَوْلُهُ بِيَمِينِهِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>-<span class="c5"> فَإِنْ نَكَلَ:</span> حُكِمَ عَلَيْهِ بِسُؤَالِ مُدَّعٍ، فِي مَالٍ وَمَا يُقْصَدُ بِهِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَيُسْتَحْلَفُ فِي كُلِّ حَقِّ آدَمِيٍّ سِوَى:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>- نِكَاحٍ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>- وَرَجْعَةٍ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>- وَنَسَبٍ، وَنَحْوِهَا.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>- لَا فِي حَقِّ اللهِ؛ كَحَدٍّ، وَعِبَادَةٍ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَاليَمِينُ المَشْرُوعَةُ:</span> بِاللهِ وَحْدَهُ أَوْ صِفَتِهِ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>- وَيُحْكَمُ بِالبَيِّنَةِ بَعْدَ التَّحْلِيفِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَشُرِطَ:</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>-<span class="c5"> فِي بَيِّنَةٍ:</span> عَدَالَةٌ ظَاهِراً،<span class="c5"> وَفِي غَيْرِ نِكَاحٍ:</span> بَاطِناً أَيْضاً.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَفِي مُزَكٍّ:</span> مَعْرِفَةُ جَرْحٍ وَتَعْدِيلٍ، وَمَعْرِفَةُ حَاكِمٍ خِبْرَتَهُ البَاطِنَةَ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>